==Trivia==
*There is currently a glitch that will cause the player's cannon to disappear if a barrel respawns on top of it. Logging out and back in again will not cause it to reappear; it must be reobtained (for free) from [[Nulodion]].
*In ''RuneScape Classic'', instead of [[note|noted items]], the barrels gave {{RSCL|certificate}}s (an early version of bank notes that only worked for a small subset of items). The barrels could drop every type of certificate that existed prior to the release of Legends' Quest. When ''RuneScape 2'' was launched, certificates were replaced with notes, in smaller quantities.

